    <item>
      <title>为波动做好准备，期待年底反弹：奥登</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-05/prepare-for-volatility-expect-year-end-rally-oden-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰银行财富和个人银行业务主管 Racquel Oden 告诉客户要做好应对波动的准备，继续投资市场。她还预测到今年年底利率将至少下调 75 个基点。她在“未平仓合约”节目中与彭博社的 Sonali Basak、Matt Miller 和 Katie Greifeld 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-05/prepare-for-volatility-expect-year-end-rally-oden-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 15:07:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
